work than theyre worth requiring you to constantly adjust vents turn on fans or repeatedly wipe the lens active antifog technology works without you having to do anything because the lens is continuously powered—never allowing fog to form in the first place klair™ modes in the abom goggle active mode always oneliminates fog all day boost mode on demandeliminates fog when you need it products the abom goggle choose a colorway features the abom one button two modes no fog all day worldclass carl zeiss lens  hour rechargeable battery  hours to full charge micro usb cable included easy swap lens system for optimum vision in any light conditions weatherproofed tech specs lightweight elastopolymer frame matte interior for reduced glare polycarbonate lens with antiscratch coating adjustable memory knit strap helmet compatible fits most adult faces one year limited warranty abominable labs abom goggles from active junky on vimeo about us abom is a group of inventors scientists and designers on a mission to make the future more fun were using our superpowers to create worldclass gear and solve the problems that get in the way of good times order now contact us send us a message give us a problem to solve or just say hey send thanks well get in touch more info p abom abom inc headquarters  sw varns roadsuite tigard oregon  technology  products  about  shop abom  dealer locator  dealer login  news warranty  support  product registration  returns  payment methods  terms  conditions  intellectual property  contact   copyright  abom inc all rights reserved bing places for business bing places for business sign in using your microsoft account work account google account facebook account dont have an account create one